Roundcube plugins
=================
My plugins for the webmailer Roundcube (http://roundcube.net).
All plugins work with version 0.5.3.


Plugins
-------
* multiple_smtp_server: Set multiple SMTP server as counterparts of set IMAP
  mail hosts.

* shortmail_character_limiter: Limit the characters of an email to 500 if the
  used IMAP host is shortmail.
